title: Blues Media Player 24.08.2013
description:
Blues Media Player is a media player for Windows which can play a large number of formats. The program supports subtitles, CUE Sheet and provides several ways to control the playback of files. Player includes built-in support for all the most popular audio formats.It supports the DirectSound and WASAPI audio interfaces.

- Audio Converter (MP3, FLAC, APE, AAC, WAV, M4A, WMA, OGG, AC3, TTA, MPC, AIFF, RA)
- Video Converter (AVI, MPG, FLV, MKV, MP4, WMV, 3GP, MOV, VOB)
